 inactive in a future release. Property type is dateTime. Note that the status property may also be used to indicate that a concept is deprecated</td></tr><tr><td>retirementDate</td><td>retirementDate</td><td>http://hl7.org/fhir/concept-properties#retirementDate</td><td>dateTime</td><td>The date at which a concept was retired</td></tr><tr><td>macroEtatAdministratif</td><td>macroEtatAdministratif</td><td>https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/concept-properties#macroEtatAdministratif</td><td>Coding</td><td>Macro-état administratif (actif ou inactif) du code concept</td></tr><tr><td>finess</td><td>finess</td><td>https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/concept-properties#finess</td><td>boolean</td><td>Permet de définir les codes concepts utilisés par FINESS+</td></tr></table><p><b>Concepts</b></p><p>This case-insensitive code system <code>https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/CodeSystem/tre-r365-etat-objet</code> defines the following codes:</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Affichage</b></td><td><b>dateValid</b></td><td><b>dateMaj</b></td><td><b>status</b></td><td><b>macroEtatAdministratif</b></td><td><b>finess</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">001<a name=\"tre-r365-etat-objet-001\"> </a></td><td>Entrée dans le champ FINESS</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>active</td><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-tre-r386-macro-etat-objet-administratif.html\" title=\"{https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/CodeSystem/tre-r386-macro-etat-objet-administratif A}\">Actif</a></td><td>true</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">002<a name=\"tre-r365-etat-objet-002\"> </a></td><td>Sortie du champ FINESS</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>active</td><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-tre-r386-macro-etat-objet-administratif.html\" title=\"{https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/CodeSystem/tre-r386-macro-etat-objet-administratif I}\">Inactif</a></td><td>true</td></tr><tr><td style=\"whit